'''妊娠滋养细胞疾病'''（{{lang-en|Gestational trophoblastic disease, GTD}}），是一组和[[妊娠|妊娠]]相关的[[肿瘤|肿瘤]]。此类肿瘤非常罕见，并且出现于子宫且有生长失控。这类产生疾病的生殖细胞称之为[[滋养细胞|滋养细胞]]（{{lang-en|trophoblasts}}），产生于怀孕期间生成[[胎盘|胎盘]]的组织。

妊娠滋养细胞疾病有不同类型的疾病。[[葡萄胎|葡萄胎]]在通常情况是良性的，但是一些情况也会转化具备恶性特征，极少数情况会恶化为[[绒毛膜癌|绒毛膜癌]]并迅速扩散<ref>{{cite journal |author=Seckl MJ, Sebire NJ, Berkowitz RS |title=Gestational trophoblastic disease |journal=Lancet |volume=376 |issue=9742 |pages=717–29 |pmid=20673583 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(10)60280-2 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0140-6736(10)60280-2 |date=August 2010 |access-date=2014-01-29 |archive-date=2018-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181020011537/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0140-6736(10)60280-2 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Lurain JR |title=Gestational trophoblastic disease I: epidemiology, pathology, clinical presentation and diagnosis of gestational trophoblastic disease, and management of hydatidiform mole |journal=Am. J. Obstet. Gynecol. |volume=203 |issue=6 |pages=531–9 |pmid=20728069 |doi=10.1016/j.ajog.2010.06.073 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0002-9378(10)00853-7 |date=December 2010 |access-date=2014-01-29 |archive-date=2018-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181020011556/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0002-9378(10)00853-7 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。这类疾病对[[化学疗法|化学疗法]]非常敏感，并且有非常好的预后。

妊娠滋养细胞疾病可能会刺激怀孕，因为[[子宫|子宫]]可能会包括异常的胎儿组织。这类组织的生长速度相当于正常妊娠，并且产生一类绒膜促性腺激素<ref>Gestational trophoblastic disease: Epidemiology, clinical manifestations and diagnosis. Chiang JW, Berek JS. In: UpToDate [Textbook of Medicine]. Basow, DS (Ed). Massachusetts Medical Society, Waltham, Massachusetts, USA, and Wolters Kluwer Publishers, Amsterdam, The Netherlands. 2010.</ref>。尽管妊娠滋养细胞疾病会直接影响育龄期妇女，但很少病发于[[绝经期|绝经期]]妇女<ref>{{cite journal |author=Chittenden B, Ahamed E, Maheshwari A |title=Choriocarcinoma in a postmenopausal woman |journal=Obstet Gynecol |volume=114 |issue=2 Pt 2 |pages=462–5 |pmid=19622962 |doi=10.1097/AOG.0b013e3181aa97e7 |date=August 2009}}</ref>。

